node.text:
Taricaya turtle release! 🐢💚
These turtles have suffered greatly due to lack of human conscience, the effects of gold mining and the contamination of their habitat. Now these little ones have a new opportunity thanks to the Taricaya Turtle Repopulation Project! Mikaela said: “Every night we go out searching for their eggs on the beach before they can be taken for food, incubate them at camp and then release them back into the wild
-
-
-
Follow us @amazing.sea.world for more !! 💙
-
-
Credit : 📹: @mikaelaswildlife @taricaya.eco.reserve 
-

node.text:
The Power of the ocean cannot be underestimated. Tsunami in Greenland 😨😱🌊🌊
A video shared on social media shows fishermen off the west coast of Greenland rushing to escape a tsunami . Men start moving when they realize that the strength of the water is gradually increasing . The recording, published last few week on Licet Studios channel, shows the desperation of fishermen, who run out in an attempt to escape the phenomenon. According to the post, no one was hurt. According to Licet Studios, the "tsunami" was caused by a giant landslide that occurred about 30 km near the site. It fell about 1 km into the fjord and created a mega-tsunami that was initially 100 meters high. It was the only recorded mega-tsunami so far "
